			NoHome: I hate not having a home.
			FarFromHome: I'm too far from home.
			LoveSpace: I love having so much space.
			DislikeCrowded: I don't like having so little space.
			HateCrowded: I hate having so little space.
			LoveNPC: I adore {NPCName}.
