NPCDialogue: {
	HakariHanazono: {
		PreMision0: Do we know each other from somewhere? Your face seems familiar...
		PreMision1: Oh, hi? Wasn't expecting a visit... though I'm not complaining.
		PreMision2: This world is so strange. I'd never seen anything like it before.
		Chat0: I was thinking something... a little dirty about the two of us. Did the developer let me say that?
		Chat1: I feel like fate brought us together... or maybe it was a love god with too much free time.
		Chat2: I think I twisted my ankle… could you help me walk? I promise I won't let go of your arm.
		Chat3: You know? Sometimes I wonder if this is real... but then I see you and it doesn't matter anymore.
		Chat4: I dreamed we were doing something together. I won't tell you what. Just know I woke up smiling.
		Seguir: Follow you? Of course! Wherever you go, I'll be right there.
		DejarDeSeguir: H-huh…? You don't need me anymore? Who wrote this sad dialogue?
		Ocupada: Hehe, sorry, but I'm already following someone. Maybe next time!
		Beso: The feeling is incredible! I've never felt anything like it!, {0}, {0}, {0}, {0}...
	}
}

